PSXDataSelector.nativeStatement: SELECT * FROM PSX_TEMPLATE INNER JOIN CONTENTTYPES INNER JOIN CONTENTVARIANTS ON CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPEID = CONTENTVARIANTS.CONTENTTYPEID ON PSX_TEMPLATE.TEMPLATE_ID = CONTENTVARIANTS.VARIANTID LEFT OUTER JOIN RXSLOTTYPE INNER JOIN RXVARIANTSLOTTYPE ON RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTID = RXVARIANTSLOTTYPE.SLOTID ON CONTENTVARIANTS.VARIANTID = RXVARIANTSLOTTYPE.VARIANTID ORDER BY CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPENAME, CONTENTVARIANTS.VARIANTDESCRIPTION, RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTNAME

SELECT CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPEID AS CONTENTTYPEID, CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPEDESC AS CONTENTTYPEdesc, CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPENAME AS CONTENTTYPENAME, CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPELABEL AS CONTENTTYPELABEL, CONTENTVARIANTS.VARIANTID, CONTENTVARIANTS.VARIANTDESCRIPTION, RXSLOTTYPE.LABEL, CONTENTVARIANTS.ASSEMBLYURL, PSX_TEMPLATE.NAME, CONTENTVARIANTS.DESCRIPTION, CONTENTVARIANTS.LOCATIONPREFIX, CONTENTVARIANTS.LOCATIONSUFFIX, CONTENTVARIANTS.OUTPUTFORMAT, CONTENTVARIANTS.PUBLISHWHEN, CONTENTVARIANTS.STYLESHEETNAME, RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTNAME, RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTID FROM PSX_TEMPLATE INNER JOIN CONTENTTYPES INNER JOIN CONTENTVARIANTS ON CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPEID = CONTENTVARIANTS.CONTENTTYPEID ON PSX_TEMPLATE.TEMPLATE_ID = CONTENTVARIANTS.VARIANTID LEFT OUTER JOIN RXSLOTTYPE INNER JOIN RXVARIANTSLOTTYPE ON RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTID = RXVARIANTSLOTTYPE.SLOTID ON CONTENTVARIANTS.VARIANTID = RXVARIANTSLOTTYPE.VARIANTID ORDER BY CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPENAME, CONTENTVARIANTS.VARIANTDESCRIPTION, RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTNAME

SELECT PSX_RXCONFIGURATIONS.CONFIGURATION AS CLONEHANDLERS, PSX_RXCONFIGURATIONS_1.CONFIGURATION AS RELATIONSHIPS FROM PSX_RXCONFIGURATIONS CROSS JOIN PSX_RXCONFIGURATIONS PSX_RXCONFIGURATIONS_1 WHERE (PSX_RXCONFIGURATIONS.NAME = 'clonehandlers') AND (PSX_RXCONFIGURATIONS_1.NAME = 'relationships')

SELECT RXLOOKUP.LOOKUPID AS LOOKUPID, RXLOOKUP.LOOKUPDISPLAY AS LOOKUPDISPLAY, RXLOOKUP.DESCRIPTION AS LOOKUPDESCRIPTION, RXLOOKUP_1.LOOKUPID AS ITEMID, RXLOOKUP_1.LOOKUPDISPLAY AS ITEMDISPLAY, RXLOOKUP_1.LOOKUPVALUE AS ITEMVALUE, RXLOOKUP_1.DESCRIPTION AS ITEMDESCRIPTION, RXLOOKUP_1.LOOKUPSEQUENCE AS ITEMSEQUENCE FROM RXLOOKUP INNER JOIN RXLOOKUP RXLOOKUP_1 ON RXLOOKUP.LOOKUPID = RXLOOKUP_1.LOOKUPTYPE WHERE (RXLOOKUP.LOOKUPTYPE = 1) AND (RXLOOKUP.LOOKUPID <> 1) ORDER BY RXLOOKUP.LOOKUPDISPLAY, RXLOOKUP_1.LOOKUPSEQUENCE
SELECT * FROM RXLOCATIONSCHEME RIGHT OUTER JOIN RXLOCATIONSCHEMEPARAMS ON RXLOCATIONSCHEME.SCHEMEID = RXLOCATIONSCHEMEPARAMS.SCHEMEID

SELECT RXCOMMUNITY.COMMUNITYID, RXCOMMUNITY.NAME, PSX_TEMPLATE.NAME AS TEMPLATENAME, CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPENAME, CONTENTVARIANTS.CONTENTTYPEID, CONTENTVARIANTS.VARIANTID, CONTENTVARIANTS.VARIANTDESCRIPTION, (SELECT CONTENTTYPEID FROM RXCONTENTTYPECOMMUNITY WHERE (CONTENTTYPEID = CONTENTVARIANTS.CONTENTTYPEID) AND (COMMUNITYID = RXCOMMUNITY.COMMUNITYID)) AS ct, (SELECT VARIANTID FROM RXVARIANTCOMMUNITY WHERE (VARIANTID = CONTENTVARIANTS.VARIANTID) AND (COMMUNITYID = RXCOMMUNITY.COMMUNITYID)) AS var FROM PSX_TEMPLATE INNER JOIN CONTENTVARIANTS ON PSX_TEMPLATE.TEMPLATE_ID = CONTENTVARIANTS.VARIANTID INNER JOIN CONTENTTYPES ON CONTENTVARIANTS.CONTENTTYPEID = CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPEID CROSS JOIN RXCOMMUNITY ORDER BY RXCOMMUNITY.COMMUNITYID

SELECT RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTID, RXSLOTTYPE.VERSION, RXSLOTTYPE.LABEL, RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTNAME, RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTDESC, RXSLOTTYPE.SYSTEMSLOT, RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTTYPE, RXSLOTTYPE.RELATIONSHIPNAME, RXSLOTTYPE.FINDER, CONTENTVARIANTS.VARIANTDESCRIPTION, CONTENTVARIANTS.VARIANTID, CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPENAME, PSX_TEMPLATE.NAME, PSX_SLOT_FINDER_PARAM.NAME AS PARAMNAME, PSX_SLOT_FINDER_PARAM.VALUE FROM PSX_SLOT_FINDER_PARAM RIGHT OUTER JOIN RXSLOTTYPE ON PSX_SLOT_FINDER_PARAM.SLOTID = RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTID LEFT OUTER JOIN CONTENTVARIANTS INNER JOIN PSX_TEMPLATE ON CONTENTVARIANTS.VARIANTID = PSX_TEMPLATE.TEMPLATE_ID INNER JOIN CONTENTTYPES ON CONTENTVARIANTS.CONTENTTYPEID = CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPEID INNER JOIN RXSLOTCONTENT ON CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPEID = RXSLOTCONTENT.CONTENTTYPEID AND CONTENTVARIANTS.VARIANTID = RXSLOTCONTENT.VARIANTID ON RXSLOTTYPE.SLOTID = RXSLOTCONTENT.SLOTID
